</span></span><i><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>neurogenic disorders&nbsp;</span></i><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>(syphilis, spinal cord injury,
cauda equina syndrome, autonomic neuropathy, lumbar hernia, spinal stenosis,
stroke, brain tumors);&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
